# Walkthrough - Contact & Booking Section

I have successfully integrated the **Contact & Booking** section into the Adecos landing page. This section allows users to connect via Zalo or schedule a call through Cal.com, maintaining a premium and cohesive design.

## Changes Made

### 🎨 UI Components
- **[NEW] [LandingContact.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/prod-2-adecos/src/containers/landing/LandingContact.tsx)**: Created a high-fidelity contact section featuring animated cards for Zalo and Cal.com. 
- **Style**: Uses glassmorphism (`backdrop-blur`), smooth `framer-motion` entrance animations, and responsive layouts.
- **[MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/prod-2-adecos/src/app/[locale]/(landing)/page.tsx)**: Integrated the new section **just above the FAQ section**.

### 🌐 Internationalization
- **[MODIFY] [client.json (EN)](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/prod-2-adecos/messages/en/client.json)**: Added English translations for all contact section elements.
- **[MODIFY] [client.json (VI)](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/prod-2-adecos/messages/vi/client.json)**: Added Vietnamese translations for all contact section elements.

